rows.label: qst202502_0010
rows.name:
Confirming increase of enemy activity.
Awaiting permission to continue combat.

rows.label: qst202502_0020
rows.name:
No, it's no good.
We'll never get through them all.

rows.label: qst202502_0030
rows.name:
KOS-MOS Re:, it seems best to
withdraw and regroup for now.

rows.label: qst202502_0040
rows.name:
If we withdraw now, we risk major
damage to multiple locations.

rows.label: qst202502_0050
rows.name:
Total annihilation of hostile units
would be optimum at present.

rows.label: qst202502_0060
rows.name:
Girl, there are too many of them.
That's pretty clear.

rows.label: qst202502_0070
rows.name:
Yeah. Mess up, and we're the ones
who are going to get annihilated.

rows.label: qst202502_0080
rows.name:
There should be no problem.
All allies, please move away from me for a moment.

rows.label: qst202502_0100
rows.name:
Locked on to all hostile unit signatures
in World Tree vicinity.

rows.label: qst202502_0150
rows.name: Initiating neutralization of remaining enemy capability.
